Those who know to 'Love' and that too 'Pure Love'

00:10:12.421 --> 00:10:16.718
and that too such 'Love' where there is no expectation

00:10:17.358 --> 00:10:18.458
no desire

00:10:19.516 --> 00:10:22.672
those who completely know to love selflessly

00:10:23.196 --> 00:10:24.648
only they can be in Sahajyoga.

00:10:27.261 --> 00:10:29.947
Egoistic people do wrong acts.

00:10:30.667 --> 00:10:32.083
I am tired of them.

00:10:35.946 --> 00:10:37.965
They will start something on their own

00:10:40.041 --> 00:10:41.965
and they won't even tell me.

00:10:44.172 --> 00:10:45.755
and by doing so

