that they have been cheated !

00:11:39.239 --> 00:11:40.339
How to get back that money ?

00:11:41.808 --> 00:11:44.106
Without asking Me all the work

00:11:46.367 --> 00:11:47.414
Absolutely without asking Me.

00:11:48.554 --> 00:11:50.620
The land is so bad

00:11:50.813 --> 00:11:52.149
that they have received a notice

00:11:52.169 --> 00:11:53.717
that you cannot construct anything here.

00:11:53.731 --> 00:11:56.131
On the contrary you will be arrested

00:12:00.766 --> 00:12:04.047
Every Sahajyogi has right to tell Me

00:12:05.319 --> 00:12:06.419
and ask Me

