It is said that you cannot grow even a chicken

00:12:20.786 --> 00:12:24.559
Are the Sahajyogis even worst than chickens ?

00:12:29.371 --> 00:12:31.350
Now whatever has happened is foolishness !

00:12:32.141 --> 00:12:33.978
and for that I am not responsible.

00:12:35.837 --> 00:12:38.158
But you ask for your money back.

00:12:39.982 --> 00:12:41.969
It is none of My resposibility.

00:12:47.681 --> 00:12:49.875
Jesus Christ had said that

00:12:53.020 --> 00:12:54.254
those people

00:12:59.875 --> 00:13:01.474
make houses

00:13:02.715 --> 00:13:03.715
live in houses

00:13:04.451 --> 00:13:06.288
they should watch birds

00:13:08.750 --> 00:13:09.983
he makes his own (GHARONDA)

00:13:10.365 --> 00:13:15.062
with how much love they make a small one for their ownself

00:13:18.723 --> 00:13:20.918
and when they make their home

00:13:21.325 --> 00:13:23.535
they feel a great joy in constructing that home.

00:13:29.003 --> 00:13:32.025
He explained it in every way

00:13:32.226 --> 00:13:34.782
that you give up attatchment.

00:13:35.790 --> 00:13:36.690
This is my house.

00:13:37.961 --> 00:13:39.061
This is my land.

00:13:40.179 --> 00:13:41.512
They are my children.

00:13:43.033 --> 00:13:44.798
Even this much that it is my country.

00:13:47.725 --> 00:13:50.618
This attatchment should be given up.

00:13:50.943 --> 00:13:54.886
Then only you can be great.

00:13:57.999 --> 00:14:00.276
In the whole world you are

00:14:00.477 --> 00:14:02.012
brothers and sisters.

00:14:02.825 --> 00:14:06.577
It doesn't mean that you give up devotion to your country.

00:14:06.778 --> 00:14:07.265
Not at all !

00:14:07.948 --> 00:14:09.729
If you are not devoted to your country

00:14:10.715 --> 00:14:11.815
you can't do anything.

00:14:13.133 --> 00:14:15.525
Within you there should be devotion to country.

00:14:16.999 --> 00:14:20.669
But the same devotee to country becomes devoted to the world.

00:14:21.341 --> 00:14:23.082
If there is no devotion to one's country

00:14:23.198 --> 00:14:25.606
if there is no drop, how can there be a sea ?

00:14:27.578 --> 00:14:29.446
first of all

00:14:29.748 --> 00:14:31.862
whether there is devotion to country, is to be seen first of all.

00:14:32.370 --> 00:14:35.058
If you are working  against your country

00:14:35.400 --> 00:14:36.500
you are not devoted to it.

00:14:37.667 --> 00:14:38.767
Jesus Christ

00:14:39.264 --> 00:14:41.667
had no need to go back.

