Christ only once went into temper

00:39:00.703 --> 00:39:02.477
which He had a right to do that

00:39:02.808 --> 00:39:03.908
when He saw people

00:39:04.276 --> 00:39:06.105
selling things in the temple.

00:39:07.649 --> 00:39:08.930
Samething we have here.

00:39:10.497 --> 00:39:12.854
And if you don't go and buy anything from them

00:39:13.349 --> 00:39:14.449
they will be lost.

00:39:16.113 --> 00:39:18.845
But you only go and buy things from them because

00:39:19.072 --> 00:39:20.631
you have a habit of shopping.

00:39:21.158 --> 00:39:22.258
Anywhere they

00:39:22.628 --> 00:39:23.992
people go, they must shop

00:39:24.741 --> 00:39:25.841
is a habit

00:39:27.114 --> 00:39:28.581
shopping they must do.

00:39:28.664 --> 00:39:30.453
They will not see the greenery

00:39:30.592 --> 00:39:32.397
the beauty of nature, nothing.

00:39:33.598 --> 00:39:37.226
When I went to so many countries,you see I had to

00:39:38.089 --> 00:39:39.458
with my husband

00:39:40.321 --> 00:39:42.261
I had to go

00:39:42.553 --> 00:39:45.435
and see beautiful places like museums.

00:39:46.077 --> 00:39:47.177
I never used to shop.

00:39:48.238 --> 00:39:50.202
But when I have so many children

00:39:50.618 --> 00:39:51.718
then I have to shop.

00:39:52.128 --> 00:39:53.425
So I would go for shops.

00:39:54.226 --> 00:39:56.111
But not the way that

00:39:56.147 --> 00:39:58.135
that every place is for shopping.

00:39:58.919 --> 00:40:00.425
What is there to shop here

00:40:00.733 --> 00:40:03.980
when you have come here for your spiritual growth.

00:40:05.643 --> 00:40:07.932
In Mecca, do they have any shops?

00:40:11.928 --> 00:40:13.725
This is the holier than holi.

00:40:14.978 --> 00:40:17.331
Why should go to the shops ? I can't understand.

00:40:17.767 --> 00:40:18.667
I have told them

00:40:19.601 --> 00:40:20.507
not to have shops

00:40:20.708 --> 00:40:24.025
but you people are the ones, who encourage.

00:40:25.352 --> 00:40:28.173
who encouraged them to make money out of us ?

00:40:30.812 --> 00:40:32.799
Nothing essential to buy there.

00:40:34.089 --> 00:40:37.979
Now you have come to the holy occassion.

00:40:38.313 --> 00:40:41.827
Here you have come for your worship.

00:40:44.661 --> 00:40:46.911
In our Mahalaxmi temple

00:40:47.112 --> 00:40:49.358
there are people who are selling

00:40:49.559 --> 00:40:52.155
garlands and things for ladies' hair.

00:40:52.751 --> 00:40:54.326
But they say it is for the Goddess.

00:40:55.499 --> 00:40:56.599
And they buy there.

00:40:57.160 --> 00:40:59.461
All the people who are coming stupidly

00:41:00.200 --> 00:41:02.465
and give it

00:41:02.967 --> 00:41:04.891
to the brahmin in the temple

00:41:05.289 --> 00:41:07.316
and the Brahmin sells it back

00:41:08.130 --> 00:41:09.230
at a lower price.

00:41:09.919 --> 00:41:12.454
And these garlands are

00:41:12.901 --> 00:41:15.182
I don't know how many times sold and bought

00:41:15.314 --> 00:41:17.401
and sold and bought because of the

00:41:17.602 --> 00:41:19.808
stupidity of the people who go there.

00:41:20.841 --> 00:41:22.343
If they have to take something

00:41:22.544 --> 00:41:24.195
they should buy it from outside,

00:41:25.382 --> 00:41:27.338
not at the place where you have come.

00:41:33.414 --> 00:41:36.838
As it is you went to Delhi, you could have bought it there.

00:41:38.399 --> 00:41:39.960
or you came to Bombay

00:41:40.173 --> 00:41:42.859
you could have bought there but not in this place.

00:41:43.151 --> 00:41:46.525
We cannot make this place Bombay or Delhi

00:41:46.823 --> 00:41:48.914
otherwise why should we come here.

00:41:50.276 --> 00:41:52.097
That is why christ took a hunter

00:41:54.229 --> 00:41:58.486
and beat them those who were selling things near the church.

00:42:01.277 --> 00:42:02.377
Now they don't have

00:42:03.056 --> 00:42:05.658
I have seen, near the church they don't have.

00:42:05.859 --> 00:42:07.190
They have outside.

00:42:09.812 --> 00:42:11.394
But they sell other things

00:42:11.952 --> 00:42:14.908
like catholic church sells

00:42:15.559 --> 00:42:18.309
a wine called Benedictine.

00:42:18.510 --> 00:42:18.936
 Imagine !

00:42:20.761 --> 00:42:21.861
That is another story.

00:42:23.710 --> 00:42:24.810
Christ went

00:42:28.590 --> 00:42:29.690
for wedding

00:42:31.691 --> 00:42:34.018
and they had no wine.

00:42:34.519 --> 00:42:36.137
Now in the Hibru language

00:42:36.363 --> 00:42:37.521
wine

00:42:37.722 --> 00:42:39.224
means

00:42:39.640 --> 00:42:42.094
the juice of the grapes.

00:42:42.295 --> 00:42:43.800
It doesn't mean fermented.

00:42:46.094 --> 00:42:48.883
So He converted water into black wine.

00:42:50.349 --> 00:42:51.631
You cannot convert

00:42:52.787 --> 00:42:55.442
water instatantaneously

00:42:55.840 --> 00:42:57.383
into wine.

00:42:57.605 --> 00:43:00.093
Wine has to rot , has to smell

00:43:00.133 --> 00:43:02.565
The more it smells, the best it is.

00:43:04.569 --> 00:43:08.445
But they think that Christ said you must drink this thing.

00:43:11.112 --> 00:43:12.212
He never said that.

00:43:13.592 --> 00:43:17.423
He just converted it into wine.

00:43:17.784 --> 00:43:18.643
meaning

00:43:19.140 --> 00:43:19.895
the

00:43:20.096 --> 00:43:23.987
taste of the juice of grapes.

00:43:24.683 --> 00:43:25.783
Once I went

00:43:26.728 --> 00:43:27.987
to some television

00:43:28.614 --> 00:43:31.681
and there was a very nice man in Italy.

00:43:31.895 --> 00:43:35.873
He said ,''Mother you first give me realisation''.

00:43:36.461 --> 00:43:39.064
So I said ,''Get some Water''. I put My hand into it.

00:43:39.607 --> 00:43:40.570
" Now you drink it".

00:43:40.872 --> 00:43:43.802
He said ,"It is tasting like wine".

00:43:44.205 --> 00:43:46.304
I said,"This is what Christ did".

00:43:47.268 --> 00:43:48.801
He got his realisation.

00:43:49.140 --> 00:43:52.041
Instantaneously, you cannot make wine.

00:43:53.359 --> 00:43:56.819
But if somebody dies, they will drink.

00:43:57.652 --> 00:43:59.830
If somebody is born, they will drink.

00:44:00.387 --> 00:44:03.724
At any cost, without drinking they are not normal.

00:44:09.908 --> 00:44:12.715
But the people who got realisation are suddenly changed.

00:44:12.933 --> 00:44:13.920
They don't want to drink.

00:44:13.945 --> 00:44:15.236
They have stopped drinking.

00:44:15.507 --> 00:44:17.296
Their attention has become nice.

00:44:17.607 --> 00:44:19.279
The whole thing is changed.

00:44:19.771 --> 00:44:22.032
This is the transformation that has worked

00:44:23.237 --> 00:44:26.018
of which Christ has talked, Mohammed sahib has talked

00:44:26.366 --> 00:44:29.290
everybody has talked about this particular time

00:44:29.491 --> 00:44:32.074
 when people will get transformed.

00:44:32.446 --> 00:44:34.671
But even after transformation

00:44:35.091 --> 00:44:38.372
you do not want to become what you have to be

00:44:40.299 --> 00:44:41.620
for which you have come here.

00:44:43.798 --> 00:44:45.111
You will be left behind.

00:44:45.841 --> 00:44:46.741
It is a big

00:44:55.823 --> 00:44:57.493
transformation is taking place.

00:44:59.273 --> 00:45:02.239
In that transformation also your rising is taking place.

00:45:03.340 --> 00:45:06.073
There is a big evolution going on

00:45:06.482 --> 00:45:09.332
and those who will not evolve properly

00:45:09.523 --> 00:45:10.856
will be left behind.

00:45:14.634 --> 00:45:18.336
As it is said that, it is the last judgement.

00:45:20.192 --> 00:45:21.392
And you will be judged.

00:45:22.077 --> 00:45:23.795
You will be left behind.

00:45:24.845 --> 00:45:27.793
You cannot adhere to people who are rising higher.

00:45:28.733 --> 00:45:30.704
With your weight you will fall down.

00:45:32.797 --> 00:45:34.431
So for you

00:45:36.020 --> 00:45:37.404
to understand Christ

00:45:37.642 --> 00:45:40.463
is all these qualities you must have.

00:45:41.370 --> 00:45:45.405
If you are hot tempered , alright , go and beat yourself with shoes.

00:45:46.173 --> 00:45:48.653
But if you are not, then you need not.

00:45:50.137 --> 00:45:51.176
You must know what you are.

00:45:51.377 --> 00:45:52.698
First of all introspect.

00:45:52.971 --> 00:45:55.253
Accordingly you should work it out.

00:45:55.452 --> 00:45:59.207
But this ritualism is not allwed in Sahajyoga all the time.

00:46:16.664 --> 00:46:19.381
I would love all my children.

00:46:21.135 --> 00:46:24.116
To be extremely loving and collective.

00:46:25.820 --> 00:46:27.824
Not to denounce anybody

00:46:28.666 --> 00:46:30.058
for no rhyme and reason

00:46:30.416 --> 00:46:32.848
and if you have to denounce, you should tell Me.

00:46:33.147 --> 00:46:35.016
I know what is what !

00:46:35.697 --> 00:46:39.032
Without asking Me, you should not measure up somebody

00:46:39.146 --> 00:46:40.701
and say i have measured somebody.

00:46:40.902 --> 00:46:42.838
With what ? what is your yardstick ?

00:46:45.573 --> 00:46:49.553
You yourself you are caught up in the web of ego.

00:46:51.696 --> 00:46:53.686
You cannot condemn anyone

00:46:54.082 --> 00:46:54.982
without telling Me.

00:46:55.759 --> 00:46:56.859
You have to tell me.

00:46:57.373 --> 00:47:00.283
Don't worry that this thing will disturb Me or anything

00:47:00.484 --> 00:47:01.720
but you should ask.

00:47:02.250 --> 00:47:03.833
I know about everyone.

00:47:04.138 --> 00:47:07.705
May be I have not mat that person but i can feel the vibrations.

00:47:10.325 --> 00:47:11.725
You can write to me.

00:47:12.433 --> 00:47:14.786
Many people just telephone, that is not the way.

00:47:15.301 --> 00:47:19.053
You must write to Me because I read each and every letter.

00:47:19.594 --> 00:47:22.312
But all nonsensical letters you should not write also

00:47:22.488 --> 00:47:23.721
to waste my time.

00:47:24.100 --> 00:47:29.186
.....like my father's mother's, mother, this thing

00:47:29.387 --> 00:47:34.456
is sick or is dead and her bhoot is moving about.

