All sorts of funny letters come to Me.

00:47:40.917 --> 00:47:42.494
What can I do for such people ?

00:47:43.066 --> 00:47:43.916
That is not important.

00:47:44.117 --> 00:47:46.883
All i need money, I have no money.

00:47:47.084 --> 00:47:52.080
I am depending on you for money. So please send me money.

00:47:54.586 --> 00:47:56.764
You can ask on my photograph.

00:47:58.596 --> 00:48:01.837
If you are a good Sahajyogi, you don't have to worry for money also.

00:48:05.322 --> 00:48:08.074
Or i have no child ,Mother what to do?

00:48:08.275 --> 00:48:09.370
Mother i want to have a child.

00:48:09.785 --> 00:48:12.754
Those who have child, ask them what do else they have to say.

00:48:14.941 --> 00:48:18.569
So many have got children after coming to Sahajyoga

00:48:18.638 --> 00:48:20.578
but you must deserve it.

00:48:25.784 --> 00:48:29.351
So many miracles have taken place.

00:48:29.547 --> 00:48:32.940
So many people have been cured no doubt.

00:48:34.138 --> 00:48:36.475
But that doesn't mean that you have done it.

00:48:38.253 --> 00:48:42.245
Don't get into the trap of ego.

00:48:45.022 --> 00:48:47.145
That is most dangerous.

00:48:47.921 --> 00:48:51.933
If you destroy sahajyoga, you are destroying yourself.

00:48:57.322 --> 00:49:00.739
So, today you all have to promise in your heart.

00:49:01.883 --> 00:49:03.808
Put your hands to your heart

00:49:04.205 --> 00:49:05.105
and to say

00:49:06.165 --> 00:49:08.414
''Mother, We love,

00:49:09.830 --> 00:49:12.259
We spread your Divine Love,

00:49:12.866 --> 00:49:14.988
encompass the whole world,

00:49:15.525 --> 00:49:17.772
give realisation to all the people.

00:49:18.504 --> 00:49:19.604
Will not shout,

00:49:20.779 --> 00:49:22.102
will not be angry,

00:49:22.507 --> 00:49:28.341
will not do the all kinds of rituals but just surrender.

00:49:29.410 --> 00:49:30.872
Surrender our ego

00:49:31.611 --> 00:49:32.511
surrender ego

00:49:32.926 --> 00:49:34.452
surrender your ego.

00:49:34.699 --> 00:49:36.832
All your problems can be solved.

00:49:37.257 --> 00:49:39.142
because, as long as, there is ego

00:49:39.462 --> 00:49:41.767
this divine power doesn't take over.

00:49:42.491 --> 00:49:43.591
You may do anything

00:49:43.998 --> 00:49:46.668
You are not connected. Your connection is missing.

00:49:47.935 --> 00:49:50.232
Christ is missing. He is no more.

00:49:52.654 --> 00:49:57.512
To establish Him first of all you must show how you love.

00:49:57.844 --> 00:49:58.215
That doesn't mean

00:49:58.416 --> 00:50:01.957
that you love your wife,love your children and love your house.

00:50:04.497 --> 00:50:06.584
You have to love everyone.

00:50:08.046 --> 00:50:10.772
Try to make everyone happy.

00:50:11.957 --> 00:50:13.406
That is why I like music

00:50:13.481 --> 00:50:16.595
because through music you can spread vibrations.

00:50:17.856 --> 00:50:20.764
Very good media of spreading vibrations

00:50:21.756 --> 00:50:22.856
of loving vibrations.

