But those who are musicians have to be loving people,

00:50:29.791 --> 00:50:30.858
not hot tempered

00:50:32.732 --> 00:50:33.732
not showing off

00:50:35.869 --> 00:50:38.627
not thinking too much of themselves.

00:50:40.085 --> 00:50:41.461
All these will work

00:50:42.252 --> 00:50:44.269
very well if you understand

00:50:44.470 --> 00:50:47.483
that this Divine power

00:50:47.684 --> 00:50:49.592
is so powerful.

00:50:51.574 --> 00:50:52.674
No doubt it is love,

00:50:53.468 --> 00:50:55.892
no doubt it is truth,

00:50:56.814 --> 00:50:58.468
 and no doubt

00:51:00.175 --> 00:51:04.079
if you get out of it, you will be caught up by anything

00:51:04.280 --> 00:51:06.263
and you could be finished.

00:51:08.605 --> 00:51:10.879
It is a very very

00:51:12.064 --> 00:51:17.149
powerful, effective and absolutely conclusive

00:51:18.325 --> 00:51:20.638
power you have within yourself.

00:51:21.760 --> 00:51:24.542
And thanks to christ that crucified Himself

00:51:24.910 --> 00:51:27.335
sacrificed his body for our sake

00:51:27.603 --> 00:51:29.075
that our agnya is opened up.

00:51:29.276 --> 00:51:31.672
Otherwise I could not have done this Sahajyoga.

00:51:33.995 --> 00:51:35.633
But in this area

00:51:35.834 --> 00:51:39.087
we have Buddha, Christ and Mahavira.

00:51:41.506 --> 00:51:44.120
and they had to do tapasya, tapaha.

00:51:44.606 --> 00:51:45.524
They did it.

00:51:45.725 --> 00:51:49.261
You don't have to do now, they have done for you.

00:51:54.047 --> 00:51:56.495
Now see I saw the musicians yesterday.

00:51:56.696 --> 00:51:59.004
In two three months they have learnt so much,

00:51:59.268 --> 00:52:02.288
otherwise formerly  all the musicians I knew.

00:52:02.489 --> 00:52:03.836
For Indian music

00:52:04.716 --> 00:52:06.458
had to really starve.

00:52:07.028 --> 00:52:09.271
For months together they had to practice

00:52:09.472 --> 00:52:13.188
 years together, they had to bow to their guru.

00:52:13.389 --> 00:52:15.348
That is all over now.

