because of this Param Chaitanya

00:52:20.154 --> 00:52:21.978
and your power

00:52:23.202 --> 00:52:25.560
to be one with the Divine.

00:52:25.761 --> 00:52:29.341
This Divine power can transform you completely

00:52:29.572 --> 00:52:31.255
to such an extent

00:52:31.456 --> 00:52:33.301
that anything that you want to do,

00:52:33.502 --> 00:52:35.293
you can do it in two, three months.

