00:54:14.545 --> 00:54:16.072
Because they go on

00:54:16.273 --> 00:54:17.734
taking their

00:54:17.935 --> 00:54:19.732
....tongue

00:54:20.217 --> 00:54:23.689
and lips on one side, then on another side.

00:54:29.688 --> 00:54:32.846
English of the French is another point.

00:54:33.047 --> 00:54:35.131
So best is to learn Hindi.

00:54:35.332 --> 00:54:39.878
and that too a good Hindi, not Sanskritized.

00:54:39.920 --> 00:54:43.535
But as they say (Rozmara) i.e., day- to- day- Hindi because

00:54:43.870 --> 00:54:47.096
I feel better if you understand what I am saying.

00:54:47.449 --> 00:54:49.480
It is not difficult because you are all sahajyogis.

00:54:49.681 --> 00:54:52.141
You can learn Hindi in no time. I am not saying you learn Sanskrit.

00:54:52.518 --> 00:54:53.887
But Hindi is very easy.

00:54:54.313 --> 00:54:56.155
Try to (learn Hindi). It is not My Mother tongue.

00:54:56.356 --> 00:54:58.835
I have never studied Hindi language, never.

00:54:59.286 --> 00:55:02.815
But you see it is a very easy language to learn.

00:55:03.569 --> 00:55:08.322
But as My father told Me ,"Never teach Hindi language

00:55:08.762 --> 00:55:10.257
to an English man."

00:55:12.882 --> 00:55:14.624
I said," Why this advise ?"

00:55:15.223 --> 00:55:17.612
He said," There was an English man who was after me

00:55:17.813 --> 00:55:19.486
that i should teach him Hindi."

00:55:20.551 --> 00:55:24.476
so he said," I have to tell my servant to open the door

00:55:26.079 --> 00:55:27.488
or to close the door.''

00:55:29.306 --> 00:55:32.028
So for open the door he said you say

00:55:32.816 --> 00:55:38.076
'there was a cool day', means 'Darwaza khol de'

00:55:43.309 --> 00:55:51.332
(clapping)

00:55:51.541 --> 00:55:55.838
And for closing the door, you have to say, 'There was a banker'

00:55:57.698 --> 00:56:01.165
"Maine darwaza bandh kar dey" (means close the door)

00:56:03.501 --> 00:56:05.201
But now it is different.

00:56:06.891 --> 00:56:09.759
They will pick up Hindi very quickly.

00:56:11.066 --> 00:56:12.792
Very quickly, I can see that.

00:56:13.011 --> 00:56:17.920
If you can learn this horrible Indian classical music

00:56:18.073 --> 00:56:21.846
which is so difficult, so easily, what will happen ?

00:56:22.738 --> 00:56:26.455
They can learn Hindi in no time and make Me happier every time.

00:56:26.630 --> 00:56:29.486
Not because Hindi is My language- It is not, it is Marathi.

00:56:29.768 --> 00:56:32.563
Marathi is very difficult. I don't think you can learn Marathi.

00:56:32.996 --> 00:56:34.096
It is very precise.

00:56:34.631 --> 00:56:36.747
I think that is one of the best languages

00:56:36.978 --> 00:56:39.410
to put down your ego.

00:56:41.391 --> 00:56:44.085
That is why Maharashtrians are normally not egoistical,

00:56:44.317 --> 00:56:47.654
because in their language it is built in process.

00:56:48.196 --> 00:56:50.565
For example somebody is boasting,

00:56:52.586 --> 00:56:54.828
that I have done this, I have done that.

00:56:55.168 --> 00:56:59.866
So in Marathi they will say, " Don't climb on a bush."

00:57:00.112 --> 00:57:05.090
or what we call the tree of channa which is so big as that.

00:57:06.912 --> 00:57:08.312
Then the person is finished.

00:57:08.781 --> 00:57:11.221
Like that there are many words by which

00:57:11.423 --> 00:57:14.526
you can put down the ego of the man on his face.

00:57:14.663 --> 00:57:18.079
So Marathi language has so many advantages.

00:57:18.337 --> 00:57:20.552
but I would not ask you to learn Marathi language.

00:57:20.753 --> 00:57:21.939
 It is not so easy.

00:57:22.617 --> 00:57:26.884
But Hindi you should. It is very easy, very easy.

00:57:27.085 --> 00:57:31.132
 but you must know one  thing that in Hindi language

00:57:31.912 --> 00:57:32.921
 there is 'Adab'.

00:57:33.390 --> 00:57:35.488
'Adab' means

00:57:35.689 --> 00:57:37.195
modesty

00:57:37.396 --> 00:57:39.053
and

00:57:42.022 --> 00:57:43.122
respect

00:57:43.754 --> 00:57:48.428
respect, but more than respect it is a style of saying.

00:57:49.515 --> 00:57:53.134
Not ' Urdu ' but Hindi of day - to- day talking

00:57:53.428 --> 00:57:57.044
there is respect and a way to address others,

00:57:58.815 --> 00:58:00.135
to address others.

00:58:00.336 --> 00:58:01.254
All this

00:58:02.326 --> 00:58:03.426
will give you

00:58:04.362 --> 00:58:07.948
a kind of a more

00:58:09.365 --> 00:58:11.226
flexible vehichle

00:58:12.520 --> 00:58:14.151
to express your love.

00:58:15.378 --> 00:58:19.344
Because in Hindi language we can never translate 'I hate you'.

00:58:19.398 --> 00:58:20.398
We never say like that.

00:58:21.421 --> 00:58:22.421
I hate you.

00:58:23.247 --> 00:58:25.899
'I hate you' will anybody say like that ?

00:58:27.710 --> 00:58:28.988
We cannot say.

00:58:29.189 --> 00:58:31.428
To hate somebody is sinful.

00:58:32.832 --> 00:58:34.564
So they can never say,'I hate you.'

00:58:40.027 --> 00:58:42.477
Chastity is more in Marathi language

00:58:42.552 --> 00:58:43.552
but it is a little hard

00:58:43.941 --> 00:58:46.851
because it has got such as I told you

00:58:47.392 --> 00:58:52.208
......idioms which can correct you just there.

00:58:54.253 --> 00:58:57.952
All this is just to request now if you can learn this

00:58:59.487 --> 00:59:00.487
music,

00:59:01.497 --> 00:59:02.497
which is very difficult.

00:59:03.432 --> 00:59:06.339
You can always learn a simple Hindi language

00:59:07.087 --> 00:59:11.265
which is very very easy and very very easy to talk.

00:59:19.443 --> 00:59:23.354
There are so many things , I would like you to know about Christ

00:59:23.876 --> 00:59:24.876
But this is

00:59:25.680 --> 00:59:28.047
short time in which I cannot tell you.

00:59:29.878 --> 00:59:32.919
The way He had His own priorities.

00:59:37.481 --> 00:59:40.075
Though in the Bible He is not described fully,

00:59:40.276 --> 00:59:42.285
I should say and whatever it might have been

00:59:42.669 --> 00:59:44.167
They have reduced it.

00:59:45.480 --> 00:59:46.480
May be,

00:59:46.671 --> 00:59:49.786
