00:59:50.497 --> 00:59:56.758
So one has to learn Christianity through the heart.

00:59:57.213 --> 00:59:58.213
No other way out.

00:59:59.886 --> 01:00:01.390
They should learn through the Heart,

01:00:01.591 --> 01:00:04.035
 Heart of your Mother.

